headline: AbbVie upgraded to Buy at Erste Group on Friday
summary: As previously reported, Erste Group upgraded AbbVie (ABBV) to Buy from Hold. The firm notes AbbVie recently confirmed its expectations for annual sales growth in the high single-digit percentage range until 2029. Numerous potential new products to be launched in the coming years support this positive outlook, Erste adds.
